  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e01\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464866816/h193356AB\" id=\"_r_a_10464866816\" width=\"800\" height=\"530\" alt=\"Cheezburger Image 10464866816\" title=\"\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e02\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003e\u0026#34;AITA: I Asked for Space, She Didn’t Give It, Then She Asked for Space and I Actually Respected It (But Now She’s in HR)?\u0026#34;\u003c/h2\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464874496/hFA10A7E5/but-over-time-caught-feelings-upfront-and-honest-about-them-and-she-set-boundary-fair-enough\" id=\"_r_a_10464874496\" width=\"800\" height=\"444\" alt=\"I (M) had a close friendship with a coworker. It started as a deep connection, but over time, I caught feelings. I was upfront and honest about them, and she set a boundary. Fair enough.\" title=\"\u0026#34;AITA: I Asked for Space, She Didn’t Give It, Then She Asked for Space and I Actually Respected It (But Now She’s in HR)?\u0026#34;\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e03\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464875008/h02EF4CEB/her-special-soul-holding-my-hand-and-kissing-she-even-ignored-my-request-space-needed-time-move-on\" id=\"_r_a_10464875008\" width=\"800\" height=\"553\" alt=\"The problem? She kept engaging with me in ways that blurred those boundaries, sending hearts, calling me an angel, telling me I was her special soul, holding my hand and kissing me. She even ignored my request for space when I needed time to move on.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e04\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464875264/hA0844DB9/doubled-down-and-asked-real-space-suddenly-she-flipped-script-and-said-she-needed-space-now-instead\" id=\"_r_a_10464875264\" width=\"800\" height=\"279\" alt=\"So, I doubled down and asked for real space. Suddenly, she flipped the script and said she needed space now instead.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e05\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464875520/h0F00AD5E/some-space-at-work-can-just-have-her-tickets-go-someone-else-no-drama-just-looking-out-my-own-peace\" id=\"_r_a_10464875520\" width=\"800\" height=\"435\" alt=\"Fine. I respected it. I even told my manager and HR, \u0026#34;Hey, I need some space at work, can we just have her tickets go to someone else?\u0026#34; No drama, just looking out for my own peace.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e06\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464875776/h0F7B7DC6/and-specifically-asked-hr-and-my-manager-immediately-clocked-and-now-she-has-formal-hr-meeting\" id=\"_r_a_10464875776\" width=\"800\" height=\"369\" alt=\"Then... she called the helpdesk and specifically asked for me. HR and my manager immediately clocked it, and now she has a formal HR meeting.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e07\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464874752/hE5701894/sitting-here-wondering-if-hole-setting-boundaries-and-protecting-my-space-should-have-just-ghosted\" id=\"_r_a_10464874752\" width=\"800\" height=\"299\" alt=\"Now I\u0026#39;m sitting here wondering if I was the a hole for setting boundaries and protecting my space should I have just ghosted?\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e08\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003ePeople offered advice on next steps in the comments.\u003c/h2\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464867072/h52177262/people-offered-advice-on-next-steps-in-the-comments\" id=\"_r_a_10464867072\" width=\"800\" height=\"530\" alt=\"Cheezburger Image 10464867072\" title=\"People offered advice on next steps in the comments.\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e09\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464876032/h56621BF8/nta-are-at-work-work-she-didnt-respect-boundaries-hr-should-reinforce-position\" id=\"_r_a_10464876032\" width=\"800\" height=\"340\" alt=\"NTA. You are at work to work. She didn\u0026#39;t respect your boundaries. HR should reinforce your position.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464876288/hFA6DCD09/have-be-sure-save-are-not-ah-this-sort-stuff-happens-more-often-than-anyone-would-like-believe\" id=\"_r_a_10464876288\" width=\"800\" height=\"417\" alt=\"Any evidence you have, be sure to save it. You are not the AH. This sort of stuff happens more often than anyone would like to believe\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e11\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003eOne commenter told a cautionary tale about what could happen without HR.\u003c/h2\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464876544/h0CCE375C/same-thing-play-out-with-pal-he-did-same-except-he-never-formalised-by-getting-hr-involved-at-start\" id=\"_r_a_10464876544\" width=\"800\" height=\"487\" alt=\"Dunno if this Reddit is true, but seen the exact same thing play out with a pal. He did the same - except he never formalised it by getting HR involved at the start.\" title=\"One commenter told a cautionary tale about what could happen without HR.\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e12\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464877056/hB3F468EB/with-him-she-laid-charge-sa-on-him-work-suspended-him-not-satisfied-with-she-reported-sa-police\" id=\"_r_a_10464877056\" width=\"800\" height=\"576\" alt=\"Then the woman got the hump. Fed up of not getting anywhere with him, she laid a charge of SA on him. Work suspended him. Not satisfied with that, she reported SA to the police.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e13\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464877312/h86F5E080/two-incidents-she-claimed-took-place-he-wasnt-country-he-and-were-overseas-at-video-gaming-fairs\" id=\"_r_a_10464877312\" width=\"800\" height=\"545\" alt=\"Unfortunately, for her, two of the incidents she claimed, took place when he wasn\u0026#39;t in the country. He and I were overseas at video gaming fairs...\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e14\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464876800/h41B712B5/once-police-were-aware-they-dug-deeper-and-all-claims-were-revealed-as-bogus\" id=\"_r_a_10464876800\" width=\"800\" height=\"363\" alt=\"Once the police were aware, they dug deeper and all the claims were revealed as bogus.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e15\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003eI guess HR can use their powers for good.\u003c/h2\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464877568/h39CF625B/claimed-he-dragging-moral-company-down-moral-get-hr-involved-as-soon-as-there-is-even-slight-whiff\" id=\"_r_a_10464877568\" width=\"800\" height=\"918\" alt=\"She ended up being successfully prosecuted. His employer reinstated him. They sacked him after 4 weeks because (they claimed), he was dragging moral in the company down! Moral: Get HR involved as soon as there is even a slight whiff.\" title=\"I guess HR can use their powers for good.\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e16\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464878080/hBD6B721B/respected-her-space-she-asked-and-she-didnt-return-favor-not-wrong-looking-out-well-being\" id=\"_r_a_10464878080\" width=\"800\" height=\"1095\" alt=\"It seems like she was fine with crossing boundaries when it suited her, but when you asked for space, she suddenly wanted to flip the script. That\u0026#39;s not fair. Setting boundaries is crucial in any relationship, whether personal or professional. You respected her space when she asked, and she didn\u0026#39;t return the favor. You\u0026#39;re not in the wrong for looking out for your well-being.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e17\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464877824/hD92BC1BA/hr-but-got-derailed-preemptively-went-them-ask-them-send-her-tickets-someone-else-played-smart-op\" id=\"_r_a_10464877824\" width=\"800\" height=\"643\" alt=\"NTA. It sounds like she was trying to set you up to get in big trouble with HR, but got derailed when you preemptively went to them to ask them to send her tickets to someone else. You played it smart OP\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e18\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464878848/h3C62C2F4/nta-were-smart-do-now-cant-get-trouble-sual-harassment-but-also-dont-really-date-coworkers-s-stupid\" id=\"_r_a_10464878848\" width=\"800\" height=\"494\" alt=\"NTA. You were smart to do that. Now you can\u0026#39;t get in trouble for sual harassment. But also don\u0026#39;t really date coworkers it\u0026#39;s stupid.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e19\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464878336/hC0EA9FE4/nah-set-boundary-and-actually-stuck-she-played-games-and-caught-up-with-her-s-on-her-not\" id=\"_r_a_10464878336\" width=\"800\" height=\"402\" alt=\"Nah, you set a boundary and actually stuck to it. She played games and it caught up with her-that\u0026#39;s on her, not you.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e20\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10464878592/h0B54C43D/consistent-treat-others-and-respecting-boundaries-is-not-bad-thing-werent-petty-or-trying-retaliate\" id=\"_r_a_10464878592\" width=\"800\" height=\"810\" alt=\"The situation became more complicated when she disregarded your boundaries, and yet, when she needed space, you respected it. It\u0026#39;s important to remain consistent in how we treat others, and respecting boundaries is not a bad thing. You weren\u0026#39;t petty or trying to retaliate.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e21\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003eBest to keep your work and romantic life separate.\u003c/h2\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n    